OL,6,GSoaps and continuing dramas have a
OL,7,Gstrong relationship with their
OL,8,Gregular viewers.  They are part of
OL,9,Gdaily or weekly routines.  Break that
OL,10,Groutine and the bond with viewers can
OL,11,Gbe broken.
OL,13,FFor some time, there has been
OL,14,Fspeculation concerning EastEnders and
OL,15,Fthe long-term decline in its ratings.
OL,17,FIn general, of course, it's important
OL,18,Fto remember that what really matters
OL,19,Fis how many people overall see the
OL,20,Fprogramme ` including iPlayer hits `
OL,21,Fand not just the overnight ratings.
