OL,6,FBut the BBC's scheduling of its soaps
OL,7,Fand continuing dramas has become
OL,8,Fsomewhat erratic. It isn't just an
OL,9,FEastEnders issue.
OL,11,FCasualty disappeared for several
OL,12,Fweeks during the autumn.
OL,14,FThe revival of Waterloo Road was, in
OL,15,Feffect, the replacement for
OL,16,FCasualty's sister programme Holby
OL,17,FCity. Its first season has now ended
OL,18,Fafter barely a month-and-a-half. It
OL,19,Fwill return but the date has not been
OL,20,Fconfirmed.
