OL,6,FThe respected writer Russell T.
OL,7,FDavies recently suggested the number
OL,8,Fof episodes of EastEnders should be
OL,9,Fscaled back. Certainly it could open
OL,10,Fup slots in the schedule and you
OL,11,Fmight wonder if it might be easier
OL,12,Ffor those with busy lives to follow
OL,13,Fsoaps again if there were fewer
OL,14,Fepisodes.
OL,16,FYou also wonder if Casualty could be
OL,17,Frevived if it was, once again, an
OL,18,Fannual series of ` say ` 13 episodes.
OL,20,FOf course any moves like these would
OL,21,Fbe difficult and no doubt
OL,22,Fcontroversial.
