OL,6,FBut Is it simply the case that the
OL,7,Fmarket is saturated and that ITV has
OL,8,Fthe upper hand? Should the BBC put up
OL,9,Fa white flag and accept there are
OL,10,Fother ways to win ratings? Or should
OL,11,Fongoing dramas remain part of the mix
OL,12,Fas they can connect with people the
OL,13,Fcorporation sometimes struggles to
OL,14,Freach?
